  "title": "Talent Acquisition INT/ TEMP",
  "description": "<p>This is an internal hire for Octomate Staffing by HRnetGroup! </p><p>Are you energetic and passionate about connecting talent with opportunity?</p><p><u>Learning opportunities:</u></p><p>We strongly believe in cultivating a learning culture. You will be teamed up with mentors throughout your journey who are some of the best in the HR industry.</p><ul><li>Assist in the full recruitment process from job posting to placements</li><li>Assess diverse resumes and career backgrounds to identify suitable candidates</li><li>Stay ahead of job market and industry developments</li><li>Strengthen communication and interpersonal skills </li></ul><p><u>Job description:</u></p><ul><li>Post job advertisements and assist in maintaining candidate database</li><li>Support consultants in sourcing and screening candidates</li><li>Liaise and coordinate with candidates and clients on offers, onboarding and work arrangements</li></ul><p><u>Who we are looking for:</u></p><ul><li>Strong and confident communicator</li><li>Driven and ambitious individuals who thrive in a collaborative, fast-paced environment</li><li>Able to commit for minimally 3 months</li><li>Completed GCE A-Level / Diploma / Degree (any field)</li></ul><p>Work location: Orchard<br />Working Schedule: Monday - Friday, 8.30am - 5.30pm<br /><em>*We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em></p>",
